{"tid":2416504,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"醫護街站反安心 警恐嚇犯聚","createTime":"2021-02-21T06:13:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-21T07:20:56.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ccfeda1b889c8c8b39fbc98922118f2c385f0efc","tid":2416504,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T06:13:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210221/LCKTVWPIJVGJ5LGRKWUJUNKNGQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210221%2FLCKTVWPIJVGJ5LGRKWUJUNKNGQ%2F&d=0FWZMlR46yIxX%2BJDTULvnd%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=b0b40825\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210221%2FLCKTVWPIJVGJ5LGRKWUJUNKNGQ%2F&h=7339dc7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210221/LCKTVWPIJVGJ5LGRKWUJUNKNGQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n醫護街站反安心 警恐嚇犯聚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/AOTbSQE0DfTa2IVqqJgOG_zsyq0=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/R2CXSPRFS5FYVEVIWUZW2UQLHE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FAOTbSQE0DfTa2IVqqJgOG_zsyq0%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FR2CXSPRFS5FYVEVIWUZW2UQLHE.jpg&h=6c96db24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■警昨日查醫管局員工陣線街站。醫管局員工陣線fb圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】醫管局員工陣線連日設街站呼籲公眾杯葛「安心出行」應用程式，遭政府出聲明譴責後，員工陣線昨聯同賢學思政再在銅鑼灣擺街站，被警方派人全程錄影監控，並威脅會發限聚令告票。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n登記身份證兼錄影<br />\n<br />\n醫管局員工陣線昨聯同賢學思政在銅鑼灣設街站，向途人講解安心出行對自由及私隱影響。員工陣線副主席陳國誠指，街站未開始，警方已到場登記他及賢學思政代表的身份證。警員稱由於賢學思政過去言論，有需要全程錄影，並警告如人群聚集，會發限聚令告票，但最終無檢控。陳說日前陣線在旺角設街站後，即被醫管局及創科局發聲明譴責，他們繼續和政府唱反調，秋後算賬風險必增加，但「唔擔心得咁多」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，香港中學生關注組聯盟昨與沙田區議員黃文萱在沙田第一城擺街站，反對國民教育及派發防疫物資，被十多名警員包圍，警告他們違限聚令，要求各人在半小時內「收檔」，但未幾第二批警員到場，向黃文萱等七人發告票。黃文萱助理聞曾反駁警方，指當時街站已分散開，兩人為一組，相隔1.5米，並無違反限聚令，但警方無理會。黃文萱表明不打算繳交罰款。警方稱，昨午約2時起有人在沙田銀城街與百得街交界聚集，疑違限聚令，作出口頭警告後無效，遂向一男六女，年齡介乎16至37歲， 發出定額罰款通知書。"},{"pid":"f667a60b6added29031840500078f50e3a254f4e","tid":2416504,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T06:17:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ab1c141396583a90167d21b5e0432babf2ae05f","tid":2416504,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T06:33:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acb09c20eb31f03246abd394eacf2abf8ac545ea","tid":2416504,"uid":173002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T06:36:35.000Z","msg":"抵制香港暴政恐怖組織街頭勒索。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bccc177c829e072f2ccaa03a1051f664fc8c76b","tid":2416504,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T06:59:30.000Z","msg":"死返去捉藍店啦"},{"pid":"e76da71fd7809d42171a77f648c3f9222738f5de","tid":2416504,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T07:01:56.000Z","msg":"有病唔好入HA 醫"},{"pid":"03668aa351965868dedfe26540f376726ed15b92","tid":2416504,"uid":138964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T07:05:29.000Z","msg":"限聚令<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 排隊飲飲食食既人仲密過街站<br />\n<br />\n果然夠哂光明正大 用&quot;限聚令&quot;打壓"},{"pid":"042b3d250d5d3ad54ca5fd0a153b95806381f95e","tid":2416504,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T07:11:43.000Z","msg":"支持仲企出黎的醫護<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eea1e79de4863a58bc09a27ce9a14e868508922b","tid":2416504,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T07:20:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}